<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset='utf-8' />
    <meta name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0' />
    <title>Lease Expiration Warning - Property Management Platform</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #333;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
      }
      .header {
        background-color: #ffc107;
        color: #212529;
        padding: 20px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .content {
        padding: 20px;
        background-color: #f9f9f9;
      }
      .button {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 10px 20px;
        background-color: #ffc107;
        color: #212529;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 5px;
        margin: 15px 0;
      }
      .info-box {
        background-color: #fff3cd;
        padding: 15px;
        border: 1px solid #ffeeba;
        border-radius: 5px;
        margin: 15px 0;
      }
      .footer {
        text-align: center;
        padding: 20px;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #666;
      }
      .property-details {
        margin-top: 20px;
        border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
        padding-top: 15px;
      }
      .detail-row {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        margin-bottom: 5px;
      }
      .detail-label {
        font-weight: bold;
        color: #555;
      }
      .countdown {
        font-size: 24px;
        font-weight: bold;
        color: #dc3545;
        text-align: center;
        margin: 15px 0;
      }
      .action-required {
        background-color: #fff3cd;
        padding: 10px;
        border-left: 4px solid #ffc107;
        margin: 15px 0;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class='container'>
      <div class='header'>
        <h1>Lease Expiration Warning</h1>
      </div>
      <div class='content'>
        <h2>Hello {{capitalize recipientName}}!</h2>
        
        <div class='action-required'>
          <h3>Important Notice</h3>
          <p>Your lease will expire in <strong>{{daysRemaining}} days</strong> on <strong>{{formatDate leaseEndDate}}</strong>.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class='countdown'>
          {{daysRemaining}} Days Remaining
        </div>
        
        <div class='info-box'>
          <h3>Lease Details</h3>
          <div class='property-details'>
            <div class='detail-row'>
              <span class='detail-label'>Property:</span>
              <span>{{propertyName}}</span>
            </div>
            <div class='detail-row'>
              <span class='detail-label'>Unit:</span>
              <span>{{unitIdentifier}}</span>
            </div>
            <div class='detail-row'>
              <span class='detail-label'>Address:</span>
              <span>{{propertyAddress}}</span>
            </div>
            <div class='detail-row'>
              <span class='detail-label'>Lease Start:</span>
              <span>{{formatDate leaseStartDate}}</span>
            </div>
            <div class='detail-row'>
              <span class='detail-label'>Lease End:</span>
              <span>{{formatDate leaseEndDate}}</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        {{#if isTenant}}
          <h3>What You Need to Do</h3>
          <p>Please decide whether you would like to:</p>
          <ol>
            <li><strong>Renew your lease</strong> - Contact your property manager to discuss renewal options</li>
            <li><strong>Move out</strong> - Confirm your move-out date and schedule a final inspection</li>
          </ol>
          
          <p>If we don't hear from you by <strong>{{formatDate decisionDeadline}}</strong>, the terms of your lease agreement regarding expiration will apply.</p>
        {{else}}
          <h3>Landlord Action Required</h3>
          <p>Please decide whether you would like to:</p>
          <ol>
            <li><strong>Offer a lease renewal</strong> to the current tenant</li>
            <li><strong>Prepare for tenant move-out</strong> and begin marketing the property</li>
          </ol>
        {{/if}}

        {{#if dashboardUrl}}
          <p>For more details and to take action, please visit your dashboard:</p>
          <p><a href='{{dashboardUrl}}' class='button'>Go to Dashboard</a></p>
        {{/if}}

        <p>If you have any questions about your lease expiration, please contact your property manager.</p>
      </div>
      <div class='footer'>
        <p>Best regards,<br />The Property Management Team</p>
        <p>Â© 2025 Property Management Platform. All rights reserved.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
